quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,The rivalry in worldly increase deludes you
  102,2,Till you visit the graves
  102,3,Nay! In the end you shall know
  102,4,And again Nay! In the end you shall know
  102,5,Nay! Did you but know with certain knowledge
  102,6,You shall surely see hell
  102,7,And again you shall surely see it with an eye of certainty
  102,8,Then you shall surely be asked about pleasure